---
const { phone } = Astro.props as { phone: string };
---
<section id="process" class="bg-gray-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl">Comment ça marche ?</h2>
    </header>
    <ol class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-600 font-bold text-white">1</span>
        <p class="mt-3 font-semibold">Appelez {phone}</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">Créneau d’appel privilégié : 9h–22h.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-600 font-bold text-white">2</span>
        <p class="mt-3 font-semibold">RDV rapide</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">Intervention en 1–2 h selon votre emplacement.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
        <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-600 font-bold text-white">3</span>
        <p class="mt-3 font-semibold">Enlèvement & papiers</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">Enlèvement &lt; 20 min, certificat de destruction fourni.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>